				<td colspan="2"><span>Wizards and druids dont need a lot of time to recoup from kites, 60 mana/tick ( being conservative) * 10 ticks/minute is 600 mana per minute.  It might take them 5 minutes more or less to med back to full, and in that time they are probably selling off drops, chatting, tradeskilling, or just going afk to do other things.  
