Sure we can swarm in PoN for just under what a necro would make in fire, but there are far less necro's in fire than there are bards in PoN, it's all about the competition.  And at least necro's have the option to join forces to kill stuff even faster since their dot's stack.
<br />

<br />
The fact remains that all the other kiting classes can do their thing VERY easily.  It doesnt take a lot of skill to quad kite, as someone else said, its almost mechanical in nature.  They dont have to be dangerously close to their target to pull it off either.  A bard that can AE kite effectively is in the minority, it takes lots of skill, a lot of patience, and the ability to soak up lots of deaths to get it right.  If they want to truly makes things equal then they should make other casters be within the same distance as our ae song range to do their thing.  An AE song that requires you to be standing on top of a mob to have it work is completely useless.  period.
